  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Your sword points to your mouse! Swing your sword using your mouse to
    attack enemies. \n- Don't let the mouse stray too far from yourself!\n- Wait
    for the charge meter fill up for maximum effectiveness.\n\nPress *SPACE* to dash
    and *F* to use special items, once you buy them. *WASD* to move. \n- Once unlocked,
    *R* to use Deflection, *RIGHT CLICK* to use Chucking Cheese. These are abilities,
    explained below\n\nDefeated enemies drop food. Pick drops up by stepping on them,
    and put them in your lunchbox (green box on the floor) by pressing *E* near it
    while holding food. Collect as much food as you can!\n\nWhen a round is over,
    your collected drops are converted into \"food scraps.\" Exchange \"food scraps\"
    for different foods. \n- Each time you purchase a food, you get a random rarity.
    Higher rarity items are stronger. Take your chances!\n- Choose your food groups
    wisely...\n- You'll probably want to hold onto some scraps.\n\nCombine 5 food
    items from your lunchbox together to create a weapon!\n- Different items grant
    different stats, experiment with what works. (Hint: a balanced meal should do
    the trick)\n- You'll craft a new weapon each round.\n\nSpend your remaining scraps
    in the shop.\n- This is where you can make yourself stronger with permanent upgrades.
    \n- Or, you can buy \"special items,\" powerups which grant effects upon consumption.
    You may hold one special item per round, so choose wisely.\n\nFight, craft, and
    repeat until you fall! Your enemies are only getting stronger. When you're defeated,
    your lunchbox and all your upgrades are cleared... can you end the uprising and
    find your mommy?"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8911ed90a8343714aae2e52f88862581, type: 2}
